description:
ThemeFixer

This plugin introduces a workaround for Discord's theme bug in Enmity (light theme/AMOLED bug). It applies your theme settings on each startup.

Download: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/amsyarasyiq/enmity-theme-fixer/main/dist/ThemeFixer.js
Source: https://github.com/amsyarasyiq/enmity-theme-fixer
